prompts.frontCover: A charming cartoon-style slice of cherry pie with a golden, flaky crust, wearing a tiny, jaunty party hat. The pie slice is comically running away from a single, mischievous cartoon fork that is chasing it, leaving a trail of tiny watercolor splatters. In the center of the scene, the text "happy birthday" is elegantly scripted in a beautiful, readable handwritten cursive font. The entire design is a flat 2D watercolor painting, featuring soft, flowing colors, artistic brush strokes, a subtle paper texture, and organic paint bleeds around the edges of the figures.
